  "title": "SAP Treasury Consultant",
  "description": "<ul><li>Led end-to-end implementation of SAP S/4HANA Treasury & Risk Management (TRM) including Commodity Management, Cash Management, Liquidity Planning, and In-House Cash</li><li>Configured Bank Account Management and integrated different formats for global payment processing</li><li>Designed and executed FX hedge exposure strategies using Market Risk Analyzer, improving forecast accuracy by 25%</li><li>Conducted UAT, end-user training, and post-go-live support for Treasury and FICO modules</li><li>Integrated FSCM Commodity Management with core finance processes</li><li>Supported Universal Parallel Accounting (UPA) and multi-ledger reporting for compliance with IFRS and local GAAP</li><li>Implementation experience in SAP S/4HANA Finance modules including GL, AP, AR, Asset Accounting, and Controlling </li><li>Automated month-end close and financial reporting, reducing cycle time minimum</li></ul>",
